01:05:18,920 --> 01:05:21,000
Fourth, I think my Canelés

849
01:05:21,000 --> 01:05:24,160
are really good observers.

850
01:05:24,720 --> 01:05:25,440
Because

851
01:05:25,440 --> 01:05:27,520
in every role I play,

852
01:05:27,520 --> 01:05:28,800
and in every line I say,

853
01:05:28,800 --> 01:05:31,680
you can catch all the tiny shifts and details.

854
01:05:31,680 --> 01:05:32,880
Even if I've lost a bit of weight,

855
01:05:32,880 --> 01:05:35,120
or my double-eyelid tape is crooked,

856
01:05:35,580 --> 01:05:37,400
or I'm missing a single eyelash...

857
01:05:38,080 --> 01:05:39,720
you still notice all of it.

858
01:05:39,720 --> 01:05:41,260
You're great at noticing life,

859
01:05:41,260 --> 01:05:42,660
and great at noticing me.

860
01:05:43,280 --> 01:05:43,800
Number five.

861
01:05:43,800 --> 01:05:44,800
I think my Canelés

862
01:05:44,800 --> 01:05:47,600
are all really free-spirited!

863
01:05:48,240 --> 01:05:50,320
You came all the way to Chengdu

864
01:05:50,880 --> 01:05:53,600
and turned it into a spur-of-the-moment trip!

865
01:05:54,080 --> 01:05:56,040
That makes you truly brave in my eyes.

866
01:05:56,440 --> 01:05:57,180
Which number are we on now?

867
01:05:57,180 --> 01:05:58,060
Number six.

868
01:05:58,600 --> 01:05:59,400
Number six.

869
01:05:59,400 --> 01:06:00,440
I think my Canelés

870
01:06:00,440 --> 01:06:02,800
are incredibly loyal.

871
01:06:03,240 --> 01:06:05,040
So many of you

872
01:06:05,040 --> 01:06:06,960
have been with me for so long.

873
01:06:06,960 --> 01:06:10,040
Any eight-year Canelés here?

874
01:06:10,040 --> 01:06:10,760
Wave your hands!

875
01:06:12,400 --> 01:06:13,720
A lot of you

876
01:06:13,720 --> 01:06:16,560
have known me since my very first drama.

877
01:06:16,560 --> 01:06:18,800
So it's been eight years now.

878
01:06:18,800 --> 01:06:21,280
I often see the edits you make

879
01:06:21,760 --> 01:06:23,240
of my whole journey so far.

880
01:06:23,240 --> 01:06:24,960
And I often feel

881
01:06:24,960 --> 01:06:27,520
this journey with me hasn't been easy.

882
01:06:27,520 --> 01:06:28,960
And another thing is,

883
01:06:29,600 --> 01:06:31,640
my Canelés are very good

884
01:06:32,720 --> 01:06:35,080
at making me cry.

885
01:06:35,920 --> 01:06:38,600
Your love always makes me

886
01:06:38,600 --> 01:06:40,240
get so emotional,

887
01:06:40,240 --> 01:06:41,480
because it's so real.

888
01:06:42,520 --> 01:06:43,640
Sincerity has so much power.

889
01:06:43,640 --> 01:06:44,000
Yeah.

890
01:06:44,000 --> 01:06:46,520
The last two good points.

891
01:06:47,320 --> 01:06:49,600
One more is that you're incredibly brave.

892
01:06:50,040 --> 01:06:54,880
Amid all the gossip

893
01:06:54,880 --> 01:06:58,560
and all those different voices,

894
01:06:58,560 --> 01:07:00,280
you stay this firm

895
01:07:00,280 --> 01:07:01,960
and believe in me this much.

896
01:07:01,960 --> 01:07:02,960
It makes me feel

897
01:07:03,840 --> 01:07:05,000
like...

898
01:07:05,840 --> 01:07:07,000
it's not a cliff behind me.

899
01:07:08,080 --> 01:07:09,400
It's all of you, holding me.

900
01:07:10,960 --> 01:07:12,960
And the tenth thing is,

901
01:07:12,960 --> 01:07:14,000
my Canelés

902
01:07:15,040 --> 01:07:17,400
love me so, so much.

903
01:07:19,260 --> 01:07:19,860
Yeah.

904
01:07:20,520 --> 01:07:24,600
You've made me rely on that love,

905
01:07:25,160 --> 01:07:28,080
slowly get used to it,

906
01:07:28,080 --> 01:07:30,260
and want to give even more love back to you.

907
01:07:30,880 --> 01:07:32,400
So thank you.

908
01:07:34,760 --> 01:07:36,200
Return love with love.

909
01:07:36,200 --> 01:07:37,240
You can really feel

910
01:07:37,240 --> 01:07:38,800
the love overflowing

911
01:07:38,800 --> 01:07:40,600
between Lusi and her Canelés.

912
01:07:41,060 --> 01:07:42,560
I hope you'll carry

913
01:07:42,560 --> 01:07:44,080
these ten good things forward,

914
01:07:44,080 --> 01:07:46,080
and create even more

915
01:07:46,080 --> 01:07:47,760
beautiful, love-filled moments with Lusi.

916
01:07:49,960 --> 01:07:51,880
Let's spin the wheel one last time.

917
01:07:53,520 --> 01:07:54,480
The final one.

918
01:07:54,480 --> 01:07:55,060
What do you all want to see?

919
01:07:55,060 --> 01:07:55,840
Which one do you want?

920
01:07:56,520 --> 01:07:57,600
Which one?

921
01:07:57,600 --> 01:07:58,720
The hand dance?

922
01:07:59,240 --> 01:08:00,680
Instant photos?

923
01:08:02,960 --> 01:08:03,760
Which do you want?

924
01:08:05,260 --> 01:08:07,260
Photos...

925
01:08:11,120 --> 01:08:12,080
Magic!

926
01:08:12,440 --> 01:08:13,520
How magical is this!

927
01:08:16,560 --> 01:08:19,400
What hand sign should we all do together?

928
01:08:19,400 --> 01:08:22,060
Let's do a special one, okay?

929
01:08:22,060 --> 01:08:22,360
Okay.

930
01:08:22,360 --> 01:08:23,920
A heart?

931
01:08:24,340 --> 01:08:24,900
Okay.

932
01:08:25,900 --> 01:08:26,880
All right, hearts it is.

933
01:08:26,880 --> 01:08:28,000
Everyone, make a heart.

934
01:08:28,620 --> 01:08:31,500
Three, two, one.

935
01:08:33,080 --> 01:08:35,600
It's coming out.

936
01:08:36,680 --> 01:08:37,520
Okay, Lusi,

937
01:08:37,520 --> 01:08:39,600
wait for it to develop.

938
01:08:40,040 --> 01:08:40,920
Now this side.

939
01:08:45,340 --> 01:08:47,060
All right, friends on this side, get ready.

940
01:08:47,880 --> 01:08:49,720
And friends on the third floor too.

941
01:08:50,840 --> 01:08:52,480
Even her backs look great.

942
01:08:52,480 --> 01:08:54,120
Do you want back view or front view?

943
01:08:54,120 --> 01:08:55,320
Back view works too.

944
01:08:56,100 --> 01:08:59,060
Three, two, one.

945
01:09:00,160 --> 01:09:00,880
Got it.

946
01:09:05,920 --> 01:09:07,040
Lusi, hold this one too.

947
01:09:07,040 --> 01:09:09,920
In a bit, we'll watch them develop together.

948
01:09:09,920 --> 01:09:12,000
All right, friends on this side.

949
01:09:14,220 --> 01:09:18,100
Three, two, one.

950
01:09:25,400 --> 01:09:26,720
Okay, ready.

951
01:09:26,720 --> 01:09:28,720
Three, two, one.

952
01:09:31,900 --> 01:09:32,140
All right.

953
01:09:36,020 --> 01:09:38,260
Let's keep all these beautiful moments.

954
01:09:38,840 --> 01:09:40,320
All right, let's head back to center stage

955
01:09:40,920 --> 01:09:42,160
and show them to the camera.

956
01:09:42,160 --> 01:09:43,540
The earlier ones are already slowly developing.

957
01:09:45,360 --> 01:09:47,080
Each side has its own charm.

958
01:09:47,640 --> 01:09:49,080
Some are super close-ups of Lusi,

959
01:09:49,080 --> 01:09:52,200
and some are those gorgeous back views.

960
01:09:56,720 --> 01:09:58,200
I'm keeping them, okay?

961
01:09:58,200 --> 01:09:59,160
May I have them?

962
01:10:01,120 --> 01:10:03,400
Keep them carefully.

963
01:10:07,200 --> 01:10:08,400
Want to hear another song?

964
01:10:08,400 --> 01:10:10,520
- Yes! - Yes!

965
01:10:10,520 --> 01:10:12,360
Now we'll hand the stage

966
01:10:12,360 --> 01:10:14,440
back to our Lusi!

967
01:10:14,440 --> 01:10:15,080
Please.

968
01:10:18,140 --> 01:10:21,080
["River of Love" lyrics: Ma Yi, music: Cheng Jinyuan]

969
01:10:21,080 --> 01:10:23,160
Here's "River of Love" for you all.

970
01:10:26,920 --> 01:10:28,200
Let's sing it together, okay?

971
01:13:28,400 --> 01:13:30,040
So beautiful, right?

972
01:13:30,480 --> 01:13:31,920
Yes!

973
01:13:32,240 --> 01:13:33,040
Really?

974
01:13:33,720 --> 01:13:34,720
Lusi, why did you pick this song?

975
01:13:34,720 --> 01:13:35,840
Share with us.

976
01:13:36,640 --> 01:13:37,760
Because...

977
01:13:38,720 --> 01:13:40,000
because this year,

978
01:13:40,000 --> 01:13:42,760
it's almost ten years

979
01:13:42,760 --> 01:13:44,240
since I debuted.

980
01:13:44,680 --> 01:13:45,560
And...

981
01:13:46,240 --> 01:13:48,760
there's this feeling that's been slowly growing

982
01:13:48,760 --> 01:13:50,880
through my acting journey

983
01:13:50,880 --> 01:13:53,120
and all the time I've spent

984
01:13:54,080 --> 01:13:55,080
with my fans.

985
01:13:55,520 --> 01:13:57,020
Over time,

986
01:13:57,020 --> 01:13:58,080
I've come to feel

987
01:13:58,520 --> 01:14:00,520
it surges up sometimes,

988
01:14:01,040 --> 01:14:02,960
and sometimes

989
01:14:04,520 --> 01:14:06,040
it's very calm.

990
01:14:06,040 --> 01:14:08,160
I feel like it's a little river

991
01:14:09,240 --> 01:14:12,440
flowing in the space between us.

992
01:14:12,440 --> 01:14:13,680
And I think

993
01:14:14,200 --> 01:14:16,160
that little river must be made of love.

994
01:14:16,160 --> 01:14:18,600
That's why I chose "River of Love"

995
01:14:18,600 --> 01:14:21,240
to share with everyone.

996
01:14:21,240 --> 01:14:24,320
I think it suits them.

997
01:14:24,320 --> 01:14:24,920
That's so romantic.

998
01:14:24,920 --> 01:14:27,800
Just now, carried by Lusi's voice,

999
01:14:27,800 --> 01:14:29,140
the music took us

1000
01:14:29,140 --> 01:14:30,520
right into a river of love.

1001
01:14:30,520 --> 01:14:33,320
I hope we'll have more time

1002
01:14:33,320 --> 01:14:34,280
and more

1003
01:14:34,280 --> 01:14:36,160
of those tiny moments

1004
01:14:36,160 --> 01:14:37,460
where we can pour our hearts out

1005
01:14:37,460 --> 01:14:38,660
and share them with each other.

1006
01:14:38,660 --> 01:14:39,680
Next up,

1007
01:14:39,680 --> 01:14:42,280
we have a little ceremony.

1008
01:14:42,280 --> 01:14:44,400
Our fans who love Lusi

1009
01:14:44,400 --> 01:14:46,080
have specially recorded

1010
01:14:46,080 --> 01:14:47,920
a message they want to say to her.

1011
01:14:47,920 --> 01:14:48,480
Really?

1012
01:14:48,480 --> 01:14:49,680
Everyone here will hear it...

1013
01:14:49,680 --> 01:14:51,000
But during rehearsal...

1014
01:14:51,000 --> 01:14:51,880
Lusi didn't get to hear this.

1015
01:14:52,680 --> 01:14:54,040
So let's all listen to it

1016
01:14:54,040 --> 01:14:55,320
together with her.

1017
01:14:55,320 --> 01:14:57,280
- Let's hear what's in their hearts, - Okay.

1018
01:14:57,280 --> 01:14:58,000
what they want to say to Lusi.

1019
01:15:01,760 --> 01:15:06,320
[On Nov. 9, a tiny speck of dust appeared in this world.]

1020
01:15:06,320 --> 01:15:10,180
[But to Canelés, it was a star falling to earth.]

1021
01:15:10,320 --> 01:15:12,420
"This is my seventh year liking you."

1022
01:15:12,720 --> 01:15:14,940
"Without noticing, I've been with you for 2,000 days."

1023
01:15:15,280 --> 01:15:17,620
"Without noticing, I've been fond of you for three years."

1024
01:15:17,680 --> 01:15:20,180
"Today is day 261 of me liking you."

1025
01:15:20,400 --> 01:15:23,460
"From September 18, 2022 till now,

1026
01:15:23,460 --> 01:15:26,540
I've liked you for 1,122 days."

1027
01:15:27,280 --> 01:15:28,500
"Time really flies.

1028
01:15:28,500 --> 01:15:30,740
Canelés have known you for eight years now."

1029
01:15:31,000 --> 01:15:34,420
"All these years, we've watched you grow through each role.

1030
01:15:34,420 --> 01:15:37,740
Your hard work and love for acting are crystal clear."

1031
01:15:38,000 --> 01:15:40,940
"You're truly amazing. I love watching you act.

1032
01:15:40,940 --> 01:15:44,820
You said you'll act till you're eighty, so I'll watch you till then."

1033
01:15:45,080 --> 01:15:47,820
"Thanks for accompanying us with your roles and your smile.

1034
01:15:47,820 --> 01:15:51,900
Remember, your health comes first. Eat properly."

1035
01:15:52,000 --> 01:15:54,540
"I hope every day goes your way and brings you joy."

1036
01:15:54,600 --> 01:15:57,340
"May you feel ever more complete in loving and being loved."

1037
01:15:57,350 --> 01:15:59,660
"Thank you for always caring for us and loving us."

1038
01:15:59,920 --> 01:16:02,580
"Thank you for each drama and every kind gesture

1039
01:16:02,580 --> 01:16:05,180
that brings us new surprises and little bits of courage.

1040
01:16:05,180 --> 01:16:07,380
I'm also working hard to become a better me."

1041
01:16:07,560 --> 01:16:10,020
"I hope you always keep the courage to love and be loved."

1042
01:16:10,200 --> 01:16:13,620
"Get past each hurdle, and the road ahead will still shine.

1043
01:16:13,620 --> 01:16:16,260
We'll all be right behind you, always."

1044
01:16:16,270 --> 01:16:19,780
"Because of you, I've become more confident, braver, and stronger."

1045
01:16:20,040 --> 01:16:22,660
"You are brave, kind, honest, and beautiful.

1046
01:16:22,660 --> 01:16:25,020
May you always be your own sunflower."

1047
01:16:25,030 --> 01:16:27,300
"On this brilliant day that belongs to you,

1048
01:16:27,300 --> 01:16:32,140
may every flower bloom for you and every star shine for you."

1049
01:16:32,360 --> 01:16:35,940
"I miss you so much, even if we can't meet today.

1050
01:16:35,940 --> 01:16:39,660
We'll still have so many moments together. I love you most!"

1051
01:16:39,800 --> 01:16:42,140
"To me, you're like a gift.

1052
01:16:42,140 --> 01:16:44,220
Thank you for coming into my life."

1053
01:16:44,560 --> 01:16:46,340
"Do everything that makes your eyes light up.

1054
01:16:46,340 --> 01:16:48,700
Don't worry about the outcome.

1055
01:16:48,700 --> 01:16:50,780
We'll walk every long, tough road with you."

1056
01:16:51,040 --> 01:16:54,000
"It won't stop this year. Every year to come, we'll be with you.

1057
01:16:54,000 --> 01:16:54,620
I love you!"

1058
01:16:54,660 --> 01:16:57,100
"All of us will be keeping an eye on you, okay?"

1059
01:16:57,400 --> 01:16:59,660
"Lotus blooms and falls.

1060
01:16:59,860 --> 01:17:01,580
With a heart as kind as yours,

1061
01:17:01,580 --> 01:17:04,340
blooming or fading are just different ways of being whole."

1062
01:17:04,920 --> 01:17:06,580
"I've remembered your word for years:

1063
01:17:06,580 --> 01:17:09,060
'Cherish the moment, and let's grow up together.'"

1064
01:17:09,320 --> 01:17:10,620
"Thank you for choosing to be an actor.

1065
01:17:10,900 --> 01:17:14,020
Now your light rises and outshines all.

1066
01:17:14,120 --> 01:17:16,060
It'll be your era!"

1067
01:17:16,500 --> 01:17:18,580
"May you always keep this precious heart.

1068
01:17:18,580 --> 01:17:20,940
May joy and good fortune always walk with you."

1069
01:17:21,540 --> 01:17:23,540
"I'm a Canelé from Guangxi."

1070
01:17:23,540 --> 01:17:25,460
"I'm a Canelé from Singapore."

1071
01:17:25,460 --> 01:17:26,820
"I'm a Canelé from Shandong."

1072
01:17:26,820 --> 01:17:27,900
"I'm a Canelé from Suzhou, Jiangsu."

1073
01:17:33,000 --> 01:17:35,180
"You're like a beam of light in my darkest world."

1074
01:17:36,900 --> 01:17:37,900
"Keep charging forward!"

1075
01:17:37,900 --> 01:17:39,060
"Take on the dramas you want..."

1076
01:17:39,060 --> 01:17:39,940
"We'll all be here backing you!"

1077
01:17:39,940 --> 01:17:42,500
"Keep warm and don't get sick."

1078
01:17:42,500 --> 01:17:43,660
"You know what? You're truly amazing!"

1079
01:17:44,340 --> 01:17:45,840
"We're always there."

1080
01:17:45,840 --> 01:17:47,940
"You're our one and only, forever."

1081
01:17:49,140 --> 01:17:51,700
"At 27, shine in your own light."

1082
01:18:08,360 --> 01:18:09,720
In moments like this,

1083
01:18:09,720 --> 01:18:11,840
you're trying to make up my mess, huh?

1084
01:18:11,840 --> 01:18:13,040
Mess up my makeup.

1085
01:18:13,800 --> 01:18:14,320
Oh...

1086
01:18:15,600 --> 01:18:17,280
You could barely speak correctly.

1087
01:18:17,520 --> 01:18:18,320
No...

1088
01:18:19,800 --> 01:18:20,320
All right...

1089
01:18:21,160 --> 01:18:22,900
Maybe what you all feel out there

1090
01:18:22,900 --> 01:18:24,260
is a little bit different from ours.

1091
01:18:24,260 --> 01:18:25,120
Because Lusi and I

1092
01:18:25,680 --> 01:18:27,760
were standing right in the middle of this stage.

1093
01:18:27,760 --> 01:18:29,200
The whole venue went dark,

1094
01:18:29,200 --> 01:18:30,960
and all your glow sticks were shining.

1095
01:18:31,400 --> 01:18:32,600
We couldn't see the screen from here,

1096
01:18:32,600 --> 01:18:34,440
but every word reached our ears.

1097
01:18:35,480 --> 01:18:37,920
It felt like we were at the center of the universe,

1098
01:18:38,360 --> 01:18:40,120
with countless bits of love

1099
01:18:40,120 --> 01:18:42,460
shooting in from different stars

1100
01:18:42,460 --> 01:18:43,740
and swirling around our ears.

1101
01:18:43,740 --> 01:18:44,280
I wonder

1102
01:18:44,980 --> 01:18:46,180
what Lusi is feeling right now.

1103
01:18:46,180 --> 01:18:47,440
Why don't you share it with everyone?

1104
01:18:52,300 --> 01:18:52,860
No crying.

1105
01:18:52,860 --> 01:18:53,400
Let's not cry.

1106
01:18:53,840 --> 01:18:56,120
Maybe everything this year

1107
01:18:57,680 --> 01:18:58,920
hits a bit harder.

1108
01:19:00,760 --> 01:19:01,320
Because...

1109
01:19:03,560 --> 01:19:04,360
because I feel like...

1110
01:19:04,360 --> 01:19:06,760
Well, if I want to cry, I just have to cry,

1111
01:19:06,760 --> 01:19:08,240
since I don't want

1112
01:19:09,280 --> 01:19:11,640
to bottle up any of my feelings anymore.

1113
01:19:13,840 --> 01:19:14,720
Because...

1114
01:19:14,720 --> 01:19:18,760
since I was little, I've never been the type

1115
01:19:18,760 --> 01:19:20,040
to express

1116
01:19:21,280 --> 01:19:22,440
feelings like that.

1117
01:19:23,040 --> 01:19:25,200
My close friends always say,

1118
01:19:25,940 --> 01:19:27,620
"Zhao Lusi, your tongue is so sharp."

1119
01:19:27,620 --> 01:19:28,120
Because...

1120
01:19:28,540 --> 01:19:31,540
I really don't say sweet things

1121
01:19:31,540 --> 01:19:32,680
very often.

1122
01:19:32,680 --> 01:19:36,400
So today, I'm trying to change that.

1123
01:19:36,400 --> 01:19:37,240
I mean,

1124
01:19:38,680 --> 01:19:41,480
if words can carry love,

1125
01:19:41,480 --> 01:19:43,680
I want all of you to feel

1126
01:19:44,480 --> 01:19:47,400
some of what's in my heart.

1127
01:19:48,880 --> 01:19:50,400
And then,

1128
01:19:50,920 --> 01:19:51,840
actually,

1129
01:19:52,600 --> 01:19:53,440
back when...

1130
01:19:54,720 --> 01:19:57,040
Eight years ago,

1131
01:19:58,400 --> 01:19:59,800
when I entered this industry

1132
01:20:00,480 --> 01:20:02,000
at seventeen,

1133
01:20:02,000 --> 01:20:04,120
I honestly didn't know what being an actor meant.

1134
01:20:05,600 --> 01:20:07,440
I kind of thought,

1135
01:20:07,560 --> 01:20:08,480
like...

1136
01:20:08,480 --> 01:20:09,880
Back then I felt

1137
01:20:09,880 --> 01:20:12,120
I'd never get to play a female lead

1138
01:20:12,120 --> 01:20:13,780
or anything like that.

1139
01:20:13,780 --> 01:20:15,560
It never even crossed my mind.

1140
01:20:16,680 --> 01:20:18,240
Because the shows I loved watching

1141
01:20:18,240 --> 01:20:20,000
were things like "Drawing Sword"

1142
01:20:21,000 --> 01:20:22,400
and "Empresses in the Palace."

1143
01:20:22,400 --> 01:20:24,720
They all felt like such epic dramas.

1144
01:20:24,720 --> 01:20:25,720
So I never thought

1145
01:20:25,720 --> 01:20:28,680
I'd become a leading actress.

1146
01:20:29,880 --> 01:20:31,640
But there's one thing

1147
01:20:33,000 --> 01:20:33,800
that's always been true:

1148
01:20:33,800 --> 01:20:35,960
Even if only one person liked me,

1149
01:20:37,040 --> 01:20:38,760
I wanted that person to know

1150
01:20:39,440 --> 01:20:40,720
that I was really trying my best.

1151
01:20:41,240 --> 01:20:42,160
Because...

1152
01:20:43,080 --> 01:20:45,760
from childhood till now,

1153
01:20:46,880 --> 01:20:48,120
up to this very moment,

1154
01:20:50,000 --> 01:20:53,400
I feel this is the only thing I truly did right.

1155
01:20:56,480 --> 01:20:57,600
Actually...

1156
01:20:59,840 --> 01:21:01,880
in the last couple of months,

1157
01:21:04,680 --> 01:21:07,880
there were times I really felt...

1158
01:21:10,040 --> 01:21:10,840
I might not...

1159
01:21:12,560 --> 01:21:14,640
I might not be able to act anymore.

1160
01:21:19,320 --> 01:21:20,480
So,

1161
01:21:20,480 --> 01:21:23,880
being able to stand here and see you all today

1162
01:21:23,880 --> 01:21:24,840
really means a lot...

1163
01:21:31,880 --> 01:21:32,600
No tears.

1164
01:21:32,880 --> 01:21:34,940
But I swear it's because I'm happy.

1165
01:21:34,940 --> 01:21:37,220
Yeah, I really am crying from happiness.

1166
01:21:37,240 --> 01:21:37,680
Because...

1167
01:21:38,960 --> 01:21:42,280
yeah, it's all just been so hard.

1168
01:21:42,880 --> 01:21:43,520
But...

1169
01:21:43,960 --> 01:21:44,680
I realize...

1170
01:21:45,200 --> 01:21:47,240
all of you are here with me.

1171
01:21:48,680 --> 01:21:51,040
You drag me back to this stage.

1172
01:21:51,840 --> 01:21:52,840
And it makes me feel

1173
01:21:55,160 --> 01:21:58,120
that even being sick isn't such a big deal,

1174
01:21:59,200 --> 01:22:00,800
because I can still

1175
01:22:01,560 --> 01:22:03,440
do what I love to do.

1176
01:22:04,280 --> 01:22:05,040
Thank you.

1177
01:22:07,940 --> 01:22:10,460
Let's give a round of applause for Lusi.

1178
01:22:10,460 --> 01:22:11,660
Let's tell her

1179
01:22:11,660 --> 01:22:13,680
that every single day to come,

1180
01:22:14,100 --> 01:22:16,460
no matter what she's experiencing,

1181
01:22:16,460 --> 01:22:17,500
she has to remember

1182
01:22:17,500 --> 01:22:18,920
so many people here today

1183
01:22:19,360 --> 01:22:20,240
are sending her

1184
01:22:20,240 --> 01:22:23,320
endless love through their applause and gaze.

1185
01:22:23,320 --> 01:22:23,660
All right?

1186
01:22:23,660 --> 01:22:24,780
Applause for Lusi

1187
01:22:24,780 --> 01:22:26,820
so that whenever

1188
01:22:26,820 --> 01:22:27,960
she needs strength,

1189
01:22:27,960 --> 01:22:30,760
she can remember how solid and priceless

1190
01:22:31,920 --> 01:22:32,880
tonight's company is.

1191
01:22:35,420 --> 01:22:52,440
- Zhao Lusi! - Zhao Lusi!

1192
01:22:54,240 --> 01:22:55,320
Amazing!

1193
01:22:55,320 --> 01:22:57,040
I think love should be spoken out loud

1194
01:22:57,040 --> 01:22:58,680
and feelings should be let out.

1195
01:22:58,680 --> 01:23:00,480
And it's okay to let the tears flow freely.

1196
01:23:00,960 --> 01:23:02,640
The name you were shouting

1197
01:23:02,640 --> 01:23:04,920
carries so much power.

1198
01:23:04,920 --> 01:23:07,400
You're not only pouring strength into it,

1199
01:23:07,400 --> 01:23:08,680
I believe every time you say it,

1200
01:23:08,680 --> 01:23:09,940
your own heart

1201
01:23:09,940 --> 01:23:11,480
feels that same impact.

1202
01:23:11,480 --> 01:23:13,200
I hope all of you, like Lusi,

1203
01:23:13,200 --> 01:23:14,780
can bravely face

1204
01:23:14,780 --> 01:23:16,700
all the unknowns in life

1205
01:23:16,700 --> 01:23:17,760
and every challenge.

1206
01:23:17,760 --> 01:23:20,560
Just like we saw in her today,

1207
01:23:21,040 --> 01:23:22,200
no matter what she's been through,

1208
01:23:22,200 --> 01:23:24,560
she still uses her small shoulders

1209
01:23:24,560 --> 01:23:25,820
to carry

1210
01:23:25,820 --> 01:23:27,180
such a dazzling stage!

1211
01:23:27,180 --> 01:23:28,860
Zhao Lusi,

1212
01:23:28,860 --> 01:23:29,800
keep going!

1213
01:23:32,280 --> 01:23:45,080
- Zhao Lusi! - Zhao Lusi!

1214
01:23:46,700 --> 01:23:47,580
Thank you, everyone.

1215
01:23:47,580 --> 01:23:48,080
And...

1216
01:23:49,040 --> 01:23:49,760
there are many friends

1217
01:23:49,760 --> 01:23:51,320
