1218
01:23:51,320 --> 01:23:51,900
Yes.

1219
01:23:52,740 --> 01:23:53,480
First,

1220
01:23:53,480 --> 01:23:55,200
we want to thank

1221
01:23:56,040 --> 01:23:59,440
our concert title sponsor, ROSYDOEDIAN.

1222
01:24:01,480 --> 01:24:02,640
Thank you!

1223
01:24:03,400 --> 01:24:08,120
And thanks to our co-sponsor, Aaaaapple.

1224
01:24:08,600 --> 01:24:10,080
Thank you!

1225
01:24:10,640 --> 01:24:13,480
Thanks to our special sponsor, PECHOIN.

1226
01:24:14,240 --> 01:24:15,760
Thank you!

1227
01:24:16,320 --> 01:24:19,640
Thanks to our industry sponsor, moonmoi.

1228
01:24:19,640 --> 01:24:21,120
Thank you!

1229
01:24:21,800 --> 01:24:24,680
Thanks to our industry sponsor, PELLIOT.

1230
01:24:25,200 --> 01:24:27,240
Thank you!

1231
01:24:27,240 --> 01:24:30,280
I also want to thank my mom and dad

1232
01:24:30,280 --> 01:24:32,580
and my whole team

1233
01:24:32,580 --> 01:24:34,680
for the trust you've given me.

1234
01:24:35,520 --> 01:24:38,720
And thanks to all the dear friends here tonight.

1235
01:24:39,480 --> 01:24:41,680
I don't praise you often.

1236
01:24:42,440 --> 01:24:43,240
But you really are

1237
01:24:43,240 --> 01:24:44,920
a beam of light in my heart!

1238
01:24:50,480 --> 01:24:52,480
I hope you all can

1239
01:24:53,360 --> 01:24:54,080
keep getting better.

1240
01:24:54,080 --> 01:24:55,760
Every one of you,

1241
01:24:56,560 --> 01:24:57,760
keep getting better and better.

1242
01:24:58,540 --> 01:25:00,900
And I also want to thank

1243
01:25:00,900 --> 01:25:04,780
my newly founded studio.

1244
01:25:05,460 --> 01:25:06,560
May it be prosperous!

1245
01:25:07,520 --> 01:25:08,440
Thank you,

1246
01:25:08,920 --> 01:25:09,920
Mr. Li Wei.

1247
01:25:10,400 --> 01:25:12,720
Thank you, Michael, our music director.

1248
01:25:12,720 --> 01:25:14,120
Thank you to our band.

1249
01:25:14,520 --> 01:25:17,800
Thanks to the Infinity Diverse Generation dance crew.

1250
01:25:17,800 --> 01:25:20,120
Thanks to the Oh MyGod directing team.

1251
01:25:20,120 --> 01:25:21,860
Thank you.

1252
01:25:21,860 --> 01:25:23,920
In just thirty-six days of preparation,

1253
